backend.luna.lehigh.edu

Class App

  • java.lang.Object
    • backend.luna.lehigh.edu.App

  • public class App
extends java.lang.Object
    The App class creates an App object which passes in a MySQL database and stores the data in rows to be pulled from later.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      App()
      Constructs an App object which creates a new Database and Gson Object to be used later by the different routes This object is used to store the Database for each instance.
